To Start with selenium+python in virtual Enviroment, install below softwares:

On Linux(CentOS)

yum install python
yum install pip

TO INSTALL SELENIUM FOR PYTHON:
pip install selenium

TO RUN SELENIUM TEST HEADLESS
pip install pyvirtualdisplay

TO RUN PYTHON IN VIRTUAL ENVIROMENT
pip install virtualenv


TO START VIRTUAL ENVIROMENT:
virtualenv MYENVIROMENT
cd ./MYENVIROMENT/bin/activate

NOW YOU ARE IN VIRTUAL ENVIROMENT OF PYTHON RUN ANYTHING IN IT
FOR HEADLESS CODE CHECK THE TEST.py file
